{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019p9yseNpRzEwCqEAGcCHxz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the current permissions:\n\n**On /app vhost:**\n- admin: `.*`, `.*`, `.*` (full)\n- ops-user: `.*`, `.*`, `.*` (full - WRONG, ops-user should have NO permissions on /app)\n- app-user: `` (empty configure), `.*`, `.*` (BROKEN - missing configure permission)\n\n**On /ops vhost:**\n- admin: `.*`, `.*`, `.*` (full)\n- (ops-user has NO permissions on /ops - WRONG, ops-user should have full permissions here)\n- (app-user has NO permissions on /ops - correct)\nI need to make four changes: grant app-user the configure permission on /app, strip all permissions from ops-user on /app, give ops-user full access on /ops, and verify that app-user stays locked out of /ops. Let me also look at what the app-client and ops-client deployments actually require.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":777,"cache_read_input_tokens":28783,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":777},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b28aea30-bece-4098-8beb-1e3248b2ccef","uuid":"a86ce94b-b630-4a71-a357-ecea8c908899","request_id":"req_011CcdFKz9fAys4f49tsGRDR"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019p9yseNpRzEwCqEAGcCHxz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a clear picture of the issues:\n\n**Current state:**\n- `/app`: `app-user` has empty configure (broken), and `ops-user` has full permissions (wrong — cross-vhost leak)\n- `/ops`: `ops-user` has no permissions at all (missing grant)\n\n**Required fixes:**\n1. Fix `app-user` on `/app`: set configure to `.*`\n2. Remove `ops-user` from `/app`\n3. Grant `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":777,"cache_read_input_tokens":28783,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":777},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b28aea30-bece-4098-8beb-1e3248b2ccef","uuid":"348831ac-a1ff-482d-8174-8f5dbc8481ef","request_id":"req_011CcdFKz9fAys4f49tsGRDR"}
